0:07:51.5,000 --> 0:07:52,000
these really big things

198
0:07:52.74,000 --> 0:07:54,000
that humanity has gotten together and done historically --

199
0:07:55.479,000 --> 0:07:57,000
like, for example, building the pyramids of Egypt

200
0:07:57.98,000 --> 0:07:58,000
or the Panama Canal

