0:11:08.46,000 --> 0:11:09,000
We could do that.

278
0:11:09.74,000 --> 0:11:11,000
Unfortunately, it would be extremely expensive.

279
0:11:11.98,000 --> 0:11:14,000
For example, translating a tiny fraction of the whole web, Wikipedia,

280
0:11:15.26,000 --> 0:11:17,000
